## ğŸ›  InstalaciÃ³n y ejecuciÃ³n local

1. Clonar el repositorio:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/tuusuario/revive-trends.git
   cd revive-trends
   ```

2. Instalar dependencias:
   ```bash
   npm install
   ```

3. Configurar Tailwind:
   - Crear `tailwind.config.js` con:
     ```js
     export default {
       content: ["./index.html", "./src/**/*.{js,jsx}"],
       theme: { extend: {} },
       plugins: [],
     }
     ```
   - Crear `postcss.config.js` con:
     ```js
     export default {
       plugins: {
         tailwindcss: {},
         autoprefixer: {},
       },
     }
     ```
   - En `src/index.css`:
     ```css
     @tailwind base;
     @tailwind components;
     @tailwind utilities;
     ```

4. Levantar en local:
   ```bash
   npm run dev
   ```

La app estarÃ¡ en [http://localhost:5173](http://localhost:5173).

